#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:4 c365e655d9ec444f8eef268ba85fa83f
msgid "开发 Godot-FmodPlayer"
msgstr "Developing Godot-FmodPlayer"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:6 9eab769e13ac445cb06aacac77ce3f6d
msgid ""
"本页面面向希望修改插件源码的贡献者。这里假设你已经了解 Godot 4 的 `C++ / GDExtension "
"<https://docs.godotengine.org/zh-"
"cn/4.x/tutorials/scripting/cpp/index.html>`_ 开发方式，并准备从 `Godot-FmodPlayer "
"仓库 <https://github.com/LuYingYiLong/Godot-FmodPlayer>`_ 开始工作。"
msgstr ""
"This page is for contributors who want to modify the plugin source code. It "
"assumes you already understand Godot 4 `C++ / GDExtension "
"<https://docs.godotengine.org/en/4.x/tutorials/scripting/cpp/index.html>`_ "
"development and are ready to start from the `Godot-FmodPlayer repository "
"<https://github.com/LuYingYiLong/Godot-FmodPlayer>`_."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:9 7484b01a8ea94c508673267adc7f09f9
msgid "准备环境"
msgstr "Prepare the Environment"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:11
#: c5bc24ca1598470b90ff0ea36a83e43a
msgid "开发前建议准备："
msgstr "Before development, prepare:"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:13
#: bfaa04b225b64a558cc83fab9446af35
msgid "Godot 4.x。"
msgstr "Godot 4.x."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:14
#: 5f3d027d999f42ea944b170dd2219f33
msgid "Git。"
msgstr "Git."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:15
#: 8193a2d5285a495e8e098d88dd55d3e9
msgid "Python 3 与 SCons。"
msgstr "Python 3 and SCons."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:16
#: ad3ab5f3ccf140648dcbb51806f85815
msgid "支持 C++17 的编译环境。"
msgstr "A build environment with C++17 support."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:17
#: ded496ae0c974c1fbbe87a59a9098dbf
msgid "FMOD Engine。"
msgstr "FMOD Engine."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:18
#: 456cc8805a664203bb3c82612184cfce
msgid "Windows 开发建议使用 Visual Studio。"
msgstr "Visual Studio is recommended for Windows development."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:20
#: 4eb05c82178a4659855c2c8b9caf991a
msgid "克隆仓库时请保留子模块："
msgstr "Keep submodules when cloning the repository:"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:22
#: 2c03199244bd452dba410e1104172ecc
msgid ""
"git clone --recursive https://github.com/LuYingYiLong/Godot-"
"FmodPlayer.git\n"
"cd Godot-FmodPlayer"
msgstr ""
"git clone --recursive https://github.com/LuYingYiLong/Godot-"
"FmodPlayer.git\n"
"cd Godot-FmodPlayer"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:27
#: 4ab47853d19e4ae39f1fee90bf734d36
msgid "如果已经克隆但忘记拉取子模块，可以执行："
msgstr "If you already cloned the repository but forgot to fetch submodules, run:"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:29
#: e6fcae2b82124170af15d1b58a216a8a
msgid "git submodule update --init --recursive"
msgstr "git submodule update --init --recursive"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:34
#: cfc365cba187436daad697dd48addad0
msgid "选择编辑器"
msgstr "Choose an Editor"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:36
#: ae62acbef2774376808718cd714b1500
msgid "你可以使用任何文本编辑器开发 Godot-FmodPlayer，然后在命令行中调用 ``scons`` 构建。"
msgstr "You can develop Godot-FmodPlayer with any text editor, then run ``scons`` from the command line to build it."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:38
#: 44ab0a01a4024b1ea90df99ba03ac152
msgid ""
"如果你希望使用完整 IDE，Windows 上推荐 `Visual Studio "
"<https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/>`_。它提供调试器、内存视图、性能分析、源码控制和解决方案管理，对调试 "
"GDExtension 比较方便。"
msgstr ""
"If you prefer a full IDE, `Visual Studio "
"<https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/>`_ is recommended on Windows. It "
"provides a debugger, memory view, profiling tools, source control, and "
"solution management, which are useful when debugging GDExtension code."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:41
#: 89b311ee201e4fffb5356ce34aeb5f44
msgid "配置 Visual Studio"
msgstr "Configure Visual Studio"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:43
#: 53130dad24824da3bec06911380d3562
msgid ""
"`Visual Studio Community <https://visualstudio.microsoft.com>`_ 是 "
"Microsoft 提供的 Windows IDE。个人开发者、开源项目和符合许可条件的组织可以免费使用。"
msgstr ""
"`Visual Studio Community <https://visualstudio.microsoft.com>`_ is a Windows "
"IDE provided by Microsoft. It is free for individual developers, open-source "
"projects, and organizations that meet the license terms."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:45
#: e5b5c31a512f4072b8e2fd123848d415
msgid "安装 Visual Studio 时，请确保勾选 C++ 相关工作负载。通常需要安装 **使用 C++ 的桌面开发**："
msgstr "When installing Visual Studio, make sure the C++ workloads are selected. In most cases, install **Desktop development with C++**:"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:51
#: d0b06fb930d7419d8062b5a80eec049b
msgid "导入项目"
msgstr "Open the Project"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:53
#: 43086b3510bb4f0e8c30a2be538797d0
msgid "可以通过下面任一方式打开项目："
msgstr "You can open the project in either of these ways:"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:55
#: 6bfa66166476433e958b8b8e98cde3db
msgid "双击仓库根目录下的 ``Godot-FmodPlayer.slnx``。"
msgstr "Double-click ``Godot-FmodPlayer.slnx`` in the repository root."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:56
#: 0c4f8387a23740a69f594d233d316650
msgid "在 Visual Studio 中选择 **打开项目或解决方案**，然后选择 ``Godot-FmodPlayer.slnx``。"
msgstr "In Visual Studio, choose **Open a project or solution**, then select ``Godot-FmodPlayer.slnx``."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:58
#: 6848edaad0af44d3ab4343a2103b3c57
msgid "打开后，如果 IDE 没有正确识别 C++ 项目，先确认 C++ 工作负载和 Windows SDK 是否安装完整。"
msgstr "After opening it, if the IDE does not recognize the C++ project correctly, first check that the C++ workload and Windows SDK are fully installed."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:61
#: c3ca3c1bb3294c9c979623ff3c3804d7
msgid "补齐 FMOD 运行库"
msgstr "Add the FMOD Runtime Files"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:63
#: 46539eb1ace340cdb0986fe9af97cd32
msgid ""
"由于 FMOD 许可证限制，Godot-FmodPlayer 仓库不会包含 FMOD Engine 的头文件和库文件。你需要前往 `FMOD "
"下载页面 <https://www.fmod.com/download>`_ 下载 FMOD Engine，并从本机安装目录复制 Core API"
" 相关文件。"
msgstr ""
"Because of FMOD licensing restrictions, the Godot-FmodPlayer repository does "
"not include FMOD Engine headers or library files. Go to the `FMOD download "
"page <https://www.fmod.com/download>`_ to download FMOD Engine, then copy the "
"Core API files from your local installation directory."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:65
#: 412ab76d98a14fb38404497d6caae105
msgid "以 Windows 默认安装路径为例："
msgstr "Using the default Windows installation path as an example:"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:67
#: 13a114c7b25a40c6a5a2d7319bbdf832
msgid "找到 FMOD Core API 头文件目录："
msgstr "Find the FMOD Core API header directory:"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:69
#: a9bc4357e4454b7b8b53eb6efab771db
msgid ""
"``C:\\Program Files (x86)\\FMOD SoundSystem\\FMOD Studio API "
"Windows\\api\\core\\inc``"
msgstr ""
"``C:\\Program Files (x86)\\FMOD SoundSystem\\FMOD Studio API "
"Windows\\api\\core\\inc``"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:71
#: a42984b316b64ff7b90b9a50e92ca379
msgid "找到 FMOD Core API 库文件目录："
msgstr "Find the FMOD Core API library directory:"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:73
#: d490a780e7974d78af4e96195b109f54
msgid ""
"``C:\\Program Files (x86)\\FMOD SoundSystem\\FMOD Studio API "
"Windows\\api\\core\\lib``"
msgstr ""
"``C:\\Program Files (x86)\\FMOD SoundSystem\\FMOD Studio API "
"Windows\\api\\core\\lib``"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:75
#: 8b8abd6b6f1545ba84bb280ab73b178f
msgid "将 ``inc`` 和 ``lib`` 复制到插件仓库的："
msgstr "Copy ``inc`` and ``lib`` into the plugin repository at:"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:77
#: 3475c884e5304faf8afba51ccc5dc93f
msgid "``src/thirdparty/fmod/``"
msgstr "``src/thirdparty/fmod/``"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:79
#: dfc62ee082934953b3638cdd8658ea50
msgid "整理完成后，目录结构应类似："
msgstr "After arranging the files, the directory structure should look like this:"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:81
#: a9cb038f443549768bed664d8b7d9bac
msgid ""
"src/\n"
"└── thirdparty/\n"
"    └── fmod/\n"
"        ├── inc/\n"
"        │   ├── fmod.h\n"
"        │   ├── fmod.hpp\n"
"        │   ├── fmod_common.h\n"
"        │   ├── fmod_codec.h\n"
"        │   ├── fmod_dsp.h\n"
"        │   ├── fmod_dsp_effects.h\n"
"        │   ├── fmod_errors.h\n"
"        │   └── fmod_output.h\n"
"        └── lib/\n"
"            ├── arm64/\n"
"            ├── x64/\n"
"            └── x86/"
msgstr ""
"src/\n"
"└── thirdparty/\n"
"    └── fmod/\n"
"        ├── inc/\n"
"        │   ├── fmod.h\n"
"        │   ├── fmod.hpp\n"
"        │   ├── fmod_common.h\n"
"        │   ├── fmod_codec.h\n"
"        │   ├── fmod_dsp.h\n"
"        │   ├── fmod_dsp_effects.h\n"
"        │   ├── fmod_errors.h\n"
"        │   └── fmod_output.h\n"
"        └── lib/\n"
"            ├── arm64/\n"
"            ├── x64/\n"
"            └── x86/"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:102
#: a8f1ce27a18b474fb85fbe1033321cbc
msgid "不要把 FMOD 的 ``inc``、``lib`` 或运行库文件提交到仓库。它们只应该存在于你的本地开发环境中。"
msgstr "Do not commit FMOD's ``inc``, ``lib``, or runtime files to the repository. They should only exist in your local development environment."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:105
#: b706b5ff0e7c47ca98c85455f8b33faf
msgid "附加库目录"
msgstr "Additional Library Directories"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:110
#: 96df0af5deeb40e8866700a5d371912c
msgid "构建插件"
msgstr "Build the Plugin"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:112
#: 81d5d6ca1ee8477bb11c7dc61dec8a81
msgid "Windows x86_64 调试构建示例："
msgstr "Windows x86_64 debug build example:"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:114
#: aa6c9d730f544f7897efef7702bf91c8
msgid "scons platform=windows target=template_debug arch=x86_64"
msgstr "scons platform=windows target=template_debug arch=x86_64"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:118
#: 7f81b4ba50164cbaaf325ba2b92d6e11
msgid "Windows x86_64 发布构建示例："
msgstr "Windows x86_64 release build example:"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:120
#: 0e1ed3fbdcd34af18436f38681ec04f6
msgid "scons platform=windows target=template_release arch=x86_64"
msgstr "scons platform=windows target=template_release arch=x86_64"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:124
#: d82e6911ddbc4300909fa602599376f6
msgid ""
"构建完成后，请确认生成的 GDExtension 二进制文件与 ``addons/fmod_player/bin/`` 中的 "
"``fmod_player.gdextension`` 配置匹配。"
msgstr ""
"After building, confirm that the generated GDExtension binary matches the "
"``fmod_player.gdextension`` configuration in ``addons/fmod_player/bin/``."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:126
#: ef0b27aa9c0749e69484a639c2adcf8f
msgid "如果你修改了导出平台、架构或输出文件名，也要同步检查 ``fmod_player.gdextension`` 中的库路径。"
msgstr "If you changed the export platform, architecture, or output file name, also check the library paths in ``fmod_player.gdextension``."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:129
#: 74b4d41b52994c67a45c042a91701275
msgid "代码风格"
msgstr "Code Style"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:131
#: 8f2fccee303a44db877d31e8cb38a918
msgid "代码风格以现有源码为准。提交前建议注意："
msgstr "Follow the style of the existing source code. Before submitting, pay attention to:"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:133
#: 45fe664d5e4b49508f4da014fcc49a22
msgid "使用项目已有的命名方式和目录组织。"
msgstr "Use the project's existing naming conventions and directory organization."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:134
#: cdc3fdd1c8704a819f746d6b9f7b6468
msgid "C++ 代码保持 K&R 风格，左花括号跟随语句末尾。"
msgstr "Keep C++ code in K&R style, with the opening brace following the end of the statement."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:135
#: 4332f1b146bd474bbf692f6a119cc9cd
msgid "指针和引用写法跟随当前文件，不为风格偏好单独重排代码。"
msgstr "Follow the current file's pointer and reference style, and do not reformat code only for style preference."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:136
#: 663c9d9ad8e54fc4ac6ed7eb715315a5
msgid "避免无关格式化，尤其不要在功能 PR 中格式化整份文件。"
msgstr "Avoid unrelated formatting, especially formatting an entire file inside a feature PR."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:137
#: df4960eae560447ebcfadcad39be6fe7
msgid "新增绑定时，同步检查 GDScript 可见 API、文档和示例。"
msgstr "When adding bindings, also check the GDScript-visible API, documentation, and examples."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:140
#: c9152e1a859b46528b30fc71689e6943
msgid "调试建议"
msgstr "Debugging Tips"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:142
#: f7339ac5edef4e04b90424343cc32d2b
msgid "如果插件无法加载，优先检查："
msgstr "If the plugin cannot load, check these first:"

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:144
#: 076f2e27ca6341ec86f997153c1e86d5
msgid "FMOD 运行库是否放在正确位置。"
msgstr "Whether the FMOD runtime libraries are in the correct location."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:145
#: 85529ae66f6c47829bcd9ae1f7805804
msgid "``fmod_player.gdextension`` 中的二进制路径是否匹配当前平台和架构。"
msgstr "Whether the binary paths in ``fmod_player.gdextension`` match the current platform and architecture."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:146
#: 2dec39cecc09449f8a810f718da1a249
msgid "Godot 输出面板是否有 GDExtension 加载错误。"
msgstr "Whether the Godot output panel reports any GDExtension loading errors."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:147
#: 0a9b1a88c69841409e4127be04982e23
msgid "Visual Studio 运行库和 Windows SDK 是否安装完整。"
msgstr "Whether the Visual Studio runtime and Windows SDK are fully installed."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:148
#: e177a5f8a99042d0947ea2d5a08cd23f
msgid "Debug / Release 构建产物是否与当前 Godot 模板目标一致。"
msgstr "Whether the Debug / Release build output matches the current Godot template target."

#: ../../source/contributing/development.rst:150
#: 49b341c1a23a4347b5bd5cb1f2dc4c56
msgid ""
"修改完成后，建议至少在 Godot 编辑器中创建一个最小场景，验证音频可以加载、播放和停止。如果改动涉及总线、DSP、3D "
"音频或导出流程，请补充对应的手动验证步骤。"
msgstr ""
"After making changes, create at least one minimal scene in the Godot editor "
"to verify that audio can be loaded, played, and stopped. If the change "
"involves buses, DSP, 3D audio, or the export flow, add the corresponding "
"manual verification steps."
